state-STARTED-description: The task has been picked up.
error-transform-FillRef: This error occured when the tool was completing a bare reference.
error-transform-FillExternal: This error occured when the tool was completing a bare external link.
error-transform-MergeRef: This error occured when the tool was merging identical references.
report-manual-template-intro: Did the tool suggest a faulty change? Please include the following information when reporting the issue:
report-intro: You have indicated that this change is faulty. Why?
report-wikicode-na: There is no problem with the way the wikicode was generated
report-wikicode-syntax: The tool introduced a syntax error (mismatched brackets, etc.)
report-wikicode-removal: The tool removed information present in the original text
report-wikicode-template: The tool selected the wrong type of citation template
report-wikicode-template-type: The tool thinks the webpage is of type "$1". Is this accurate?
report-wikicode-template-mapinfo: The tool used page $1 to determine the correct citation template to use. Please report this issue on the relevant talk page.
report-link-na: There is no problem with the link in question
report-link-paywall: This link is behind a paywall
report-link-archive: This link leads to an archive page
errors: The tool encountered some errors. Click on the red pencil icons for details.
chancetoreview: You will have a chance to review the edit before it's saved.
